=== Noun ===
'''chocolate''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]''; ''plural'' '''chocolates''')

#(''[[uncountable]]'') A food made from ground [[roast]]ed [[cocoa bean]]s.
#(''[[countable]]'') A small piece of [[confectionery]] made from chocolate.
#:''He bought her some '''chocolates''' as a gift.''
#(''[[uncountable]]'') A dark reddish-brown [[color]]/[[colour]], like that of chocolate.
#:''As he cooked it the whole thing turned a rich deep '''chocolate'''''.

